dc_description_s: This point shapefile was created by mapping just the "center" coordinates listed for artificial reefs as noted in the California Department Fish and Wildlife Guide to Artificial Reefs of Southern California.This coverage identifies centroid locations of artificial reefs along the California coast and primarily in Southern California.
